    • Method Detail

      • stepG1

        void stepG1​(ec.util.MersenneTwisterFast random)
        Performs actions for G1 phase.

        Cell increases in size toward a target of twice its critical size at a rate of CELL_GROWTH_RATE. Cell will transition to S phase after completing STEPS_G1 steps at an average rate of RATE_G1. At each tick, cell may randomly apoptosis at a basal rate of BASAL_APOPTOSIS_RATE.

        Specified by:
        stepG1 in class PottsModuleProliferation
        Parameters:
        random - the random number generator

      • stepS

        void stepS​(ec.util.MersenneTwisterFast random)
        Performs actions for S phase.

        Cell increases in size toward a target of twice its critical size at a rate of CELL_GROWTH_RATE. Cell will transition to G2 phase after completing STEPS_S steps at an average rate of RATE_S.

        Specified by:
        stepS in class PottsModuleProliferation
        Parameters:
        random - the random number generator

      • stepG2

        void stepG2​(ec.util.MersenneTwisterFast random)
        Performs actions for G2 phase.

        Cell increases in size toward a target of twice its critical size at a rate of CELL_GROWTH_RATE. Cell will transition to M phase after completing STEPS_G2 steps at an average rate of RATE_G2. At each tick, cell may randomly apoptosis at a basal rate of BASAL_APOPTOSIS_RATE.

        Specified by:
        stepG2 in class PottsModuleProliferation
        Parameters:
        random - the random number generator

      • stepM

        void stepM​(ec.util.MersenneTwisterFast random,
           Simulation sim)
        Performs actions for M phase.

        Cell increases in size toward a target of twice its critical size at a rate of CELL_GROWTH_RATE. Cell will complete cell division after completing STEPS_M steps at an average rate of RATE_M. Cell must be greater than SIZE_CHECKPOINT times the critical size.

        Specified by:
        stepM in class PottsModuleProliferation
        Parameters:
        random - the random number generator
        sim - the simulation instance
